## Priority 4: Code Quality (Minor)

### 4A. Remove unused googleapis dependency
- Run `npm uninstall googleapis` — saves ~80MB, all Drive calls use raw fetch
- Remove `@types/express-rate-limit` (types bundled since v6)

### 4B. Generate and commit package-lock.json
- Run `npm install` to generate lockfile
- Ensures deterministic installs across machines

### 4C. Add React.StrictMode
- In `client/src/main.tsx`: wrap `<App />` with `<React.StrictMode>`

### 4D. Expand .gitignore
- Add: `*.log`, `.DS_Store`, `Thumbs.db`, `.vscode/`, `*.tsbuildinfo`

### 4E. Add accessibility to modals
- Add `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal="true"`, `aria-labelledby` to all modal overlays
- Add focus trapping (e.g., `focus-trap-react` library)

### 4F. Use FormData for file uploads instead of base64
- In `client/src/services/api.ts` `uploadFile`: use `multipart/form-data` instead of base64 JSON
- Saves ~33% bandwidth on uploads

